text: Revolution (2023) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on March 5, 2023 at Chase Center in San Francisco, California. It was the fourth Revolution event held by AEW and the first AEW pay-per-view to be held in the state of California. The main event saw MJF defeated Bryan Danielson in a 60-minute Iron Man match. The match went into sudden death overtime and MJF defeated Danielson 4–3 to keep his AEW World Championship. Dave Meltzer of the Wrestling Observer Newsletter gave the Iron man 5.75 out of 5 stars. He also gave the Texas Death match between "Hangman" Adam Page and Jon Moxley 5 stars. ==Matches== No. Results Stipulations Times 1 Mark Briscoe and the Lucha Brothers (Penta El Zero Miedo and Rey
